  m_text: "AMMETER INSTRUCTIONS\r\n\r\n1. Connect in SERIES with circuit.\r\n\r\n2.
    Red terminal \u2192 current entering side.\r\n\n\n\r\n3. Black terminal \u2192
    exit side.\r\n\r\n4. Displays current in Amperes (A)\r\n\r\nFormula:\r\nI = Current
    in circuit\r\n\r\nExample:\r\nCurrent = 2 A"
